org.hl7.types
Class ValueFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.hl7.types.ValueFactory
Direct Known Subclasses:
ValueFactoryImpl
public abstract class ValueFactory
extends java.lang.Object

Abstact base class for factories that create data type values from all sorts of sources including literal forms. A different implementation of data types would subclass this factory to provide instances of their own type implementations. A factory is made a singleton and a factory is obtained with the static method getInstance(), this might in the future retrieve a different class depending on preferences, properties, or classpath settings.
